00:28:46.079 --> 00:28:50.880
as if your organization is an, oh, really, organization. So, if you can point out the,

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:57.199
oh, really, and maybe, you know, the thing I always try to do is be high-empathy, right? So,

00:28:57.199 --> 00:29:02.800
it's not like, you're stupid, the answer is this, which I have seen done. That's low-empathy

00:29:02.800 --> 00:29:10.560
response. It's, I can't disprove it. I see some evidence to the contrary. Maybe we should look

00:29:10.560 --> 00:29:19.280
into this, that, or the other. The other thing I often try to look for is, now, that's very

00:29:19.280 --> 00:29:23.040
