the hock off. And I feel like a lot of times people replicate what they see, you know, Amazon,

00:41:21.120 --> 00:41:26.560
Facebook, Google doing. They don't understand what problem they were solving, but yet they say we

00:41:26.560 --> 00:41:30.639
